bilingual.source: Are there any lakes in the forest?
Have you ever been to a forest?

list.abstract: Forest是一款帮助你暂时远离手机，专心于目前工作的App。

yingyinNormal.en: What happened to the spirits? What's in the Forest now?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那些精灵后来怎么样了？现在森林里怎么样了？

yingyinNormal.en: They've reached Elwynn Forest. The Grand Hamlet is burning.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们到艾尔文森林了。夜色镇着火了。

yingyinNormal.en: And she lived in the forest. She was very pretty. And she had a fairy wand.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她住在森林里。她非常漂亮。她还有一个仙杖。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm pretty? You're the hottest little gopher-chipmunk in the whole forest.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我现在很漂亮？你是全森林里最性感的囊地花栗鼠啦。

yingyinNormal.en: You need to listen to what she says. Try to see the forest through her eyes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你得仔细聆听她所说的话，尝试透过她的眼睛看森林。

yingyinNormal.en: The next right thing is for me to go to the Enchanted Forest and find that voice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 继续做正确的事，是我前往魔法森林，并找到那个声音。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you think the Forest will wake again? Only Ahtohallan knows. Octa-who-what?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你觉得森林会再次复苏吗？只有亚托哈伦知道。亚托什么玩意儿？

yingyinNormal.en: We cleared the forest as ordered, my Lord. But more spiders keep coming up from the south.
yingyinNormal.zh: 森林已经扫荡过了，主上，但还有蜘蛛不断从南边涌入。

yingyinNormal.en: So George Pig and Baby Bear hopped on the dragon's back and flew all the way back home to the little house in the forest. And then it's the end.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小猪乔奇和小熊同意了跳到了巨龙的背上。然后飞回了森林，然后他们回到了森林的小屋。这个故事就结束了。

yingyinNormal.en: So, he slept forever? Yes. But all of his friends in the forest were so happy for him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以他一睡不起了吗？是的，但森林里所有的朋友都为他感到高兴。

yingyinNormal.en: Inside the forest was a little house. And inside the house was a bowl of porridge.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在这件森林深处有一间小屋。而在这间小屋的桌子上放着一碗热腾腾香喷喷的粥。

yingyinNormal.en: If you love your little forest friends, why not let them just kill my ass? What's the thinking?
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你喜欢你的森林小伙伴，为什么不任凭他们杀了我？你在想什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. But the Forest could wake again. And we must be prepared for whatever danger it may bring.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，但森林有可能再次复苏，我们必须准备好应对随之而来的危机。

yingyinNormal.en: What's tree world? Tree world is a big forest full of trees. It sounds a bit boring.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么是树木的世界？树木的世界就是布满树木的森林呀。这个听上去有点无聊啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I see. How many trees would you like? Enough to make a forest. There you go. Thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哦，我知道了！你需要多少树呢？足够去造出一个森林的！给你们！谢谢！

yingyinNormal.en: King Runeard, the dam isn't strengthening our waters. It's hurting the Forest. It's cutting off the North.
yingyinNormal.zh: 鲁纳德国王，大坝使我们的水流变急，正在危害森林，切断了北方。

yingyinNormal.en: This petrified forest is the most densely populated ecosystem on the ocean planet. A veritable oasis.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这片石化森林是地球海洋里物种最丰富的生态系统，这是名副其实的海底绿洲。

yingyinNormal.en: For what? If anyone can resolve the past if anyone can save Arendelle and free this forest， it's you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么礼物？如果有人能解开过去，如果有人能拯救艾伦戴尔，解救森林，那就是你。

yingyinNormal.en: This is obviously not the outcome we wanted. But we will resume the search the moment it is safe to walk through the forest again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 显然这不是我们想要的结果。当能安全进入森林时我们会继续搜索的。

yingyinNormal.en: What? In the Chattahoochee National Forest in Georgia? I can't be the only one that knows that's halfway.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你俩要在乔治亚州的查塔国家森林公园见面吗？不可能只有我知道那是纽约和德州的中间点吧？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
